EXACT INSTALLATION LAB (FOR CODESPACES)
ğŸ§ª LAB: Install Kubernetes using kind
Step 1: Install Docker (already present in Codespaces)

Check:

docker ps

Step 2: Install kind
curl -Lo ./kind https://kind.sigs.k8s.io/dl/v0.22.0/kind-linux-amd64
chmod +x kind
sudo mv kind /usr/local/bin/


Verify:

kind version

Step 3: Create a cluster
kind create cluster --name cka


Expected:

Creating cluster "cka" ...

Step 4: Verify cluster
kubectl cluster-info
kubectl get nodes


You should see:

cka-control-plane   Ready


